{
  "text": "Studies involving only preschoolers were performed almost exclusively in developing countries (four out of five papers), and three were performed in Africa. None of these studies reported the prevalence of drug prescriptions and only two reported the average number of drugs per patient but in a non-comparable manner [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] .",
